# responseBody.Latest_receipt_info

**Object**

An array that contains all in-app purchase transactions.

## Declaration

```swift
object responseBody.Latest_receipt_info
```

## Objects

- **responseBody.Pending_renewal_info**: An array of elements that refers to open or failed auto-renewable subscription renewals.
- **responseBody.Receipt**: The decoded version of the encoded receipt data that you send with the request to the App Store.
